            <title>[CASSANDRA-16542] 4.0 node sending a repair prepare message to a 3.x node breaks the connection on 4.0 side</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16542</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
